Package spoon.pattern.internal.matcher

Class TobeMatched

  • java.lang.Object
    • spoon.pattern.internal.matcher.TobeMatched
  • public class TobeMatched
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes what next has to be matched. It consists of current `parameters` represented by ImmutableMap and by a to be matched target elements. See children of TobeMatched for supported collections of target elements.
